5. **Type in BOTH tabs simultaneously** → No conflicts, no data loss!
6. Check the Status Bar — it should show "Live" (the Yjs provider is connected)
7. Check Terminal 2 — you should see `✅ Yjs client connected` for each tab

> **What to look for:**
