### 7 — Update `WelcomeTab.jsx` — Wire up the buttons

The WelcomeTab already has "Create Room" and "Join Room" buttons, but they don't do anything yet. Let's wire them up to the callbacks from WelcomePage:

Update `Frontend/src/Components/WelcomeTab.jsx`:

```jsx
// ================================================
// WelcomeTab.jsx — VS Code Welcome Screen
// Now with working Create Room and Join Room buttons
