   Hello from CodeTogether
   4
   ⚠ This is a warning
   ✗ This is an error
   ✓ Program exited.
   ```
7. Try an error: `console.log(undefinedVariable)` → should show red error
8. Try an infinite loop: `while(true) {}` → should timeout after 5 seconds
9. Click 🗑️ (trash icon) to clear the terminal
10. Click ✕ to close the terminal panel

