| 7 | Database Persistence | LevelDB, environment variables, dotenv |
| 8 | Code Execution | Sandboxed iframes, Blob URLs, postMessage |

**You built something that mirrors the architecture of CodePen, CodeSandbox, and VS Code Live Share.** These aren't toy concepts — they're the same patterns used by production applications serving millions of users. 🚀


